WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:05.439 --> 00:00:06.608
[ Groans ]

2
00:00:07.509 --> 00:00:09.076
Ah. ugh.

3
00:00:09.109 --> 00:00:10.979
Oh. God.
Oh. God.

4
00:00:11.011 --> 00:00:13.013
[ Urinating ]
Mmm!

5
00:00:14.916 --> 00:00:16.316
[ Glass shatters ]

6
00:00:16.350 --> 00:00:18.520
Oh. Oh. God.

7
00:00:18.553 --> 00:00:20.087
[ Coughs ]

8
00:00:20.120 --> 00:00:21.088
[ Burps loudly ]

9
00:00:21.121 --> 00:00:24.391
[ Drunkenly muttering ]

10
00:00:25.359 --> 00:00:26.393
[ Grunts ]

11
00:00:27.027 --> 00:00:28.763
Oh. ugh.

12
00:00:30.430 --> 00:00:32.534
Mmm. mmm. mmm.

13
00:00:32.567 --> 00:00:33.701
[ Glass shatters ]

14
00:00:33.735 --> 00:00:35.202
Ugh. this fuckin' thing.

15
00:00:35.235 --> 00:00:37.572
This. uh. uhh. fuck.

16
00:00:37.605 --> 00:00:38.740
Ho...kay.

17
00:00:38.773 --> 00:00:39.941
[ Error dings ]
Come o-o-on!

18
00:00:39.974 --> 00:00:41.275
Come on. man!
[ Error dings ]

19
00:00:41.308 --> 00:00:43.845
Piece of fuckin' --
piece of shit!

20
00:00:43.878 --> 00:00:46.346
[ Error dings ]
Aah! Aah!

21
00:00:47.916 --> 00:00:51.251
Hnn. hnn. hnn. hnn. <i>hnn!</i>

22
00:00:51.285 --> 00:00:53.555
[ Error dings ]
<i>Lockdown initiated.</i>

23
00:00:53.588 --> 00:00:55.757
[ Machinery whirring ]

24
00:00:58.626 --> 00:01:00.795
Mort-y-y-y!

25
00:01:02.229 --> 00:01:04.899
Ohhh. Hey. pal.
W-what's up?

26
00:01:04.933 --> 00:01:07.569
Oh. g-good --
good morning. Mor-- Morty.

27
00:01:07.602 --> 00:01:08.836
Yeah. Sure thing.

28
00:01:08.870 --> 00:01:10.772
You want breakfast?

29
00:01:10.805 --> 00:01:12.272
Or dinner?

30
00:01:12.306 --> 00:01:14.876
Are you <i>humoring</i> me.
Morty?

31
00:01:14.909 --> 00:01:16.209
[ Sighs ]
No.

32
00:01:16.243 --> 00:01:18.145
I only had a couple
of drinks. Morty!

33
00:01:18.178 --> 00:01:20.213
S-so. w-what do you
need me for?

34
00:01:20.247 --> 00:01:23.952
This fuckin' thing
locked me out!

35
00:01:23.985 --> 00:01:25.753
Okay. Well.
whose fault is that?

36
00:01:25.787 --> 00:01:27.354
Y-o-o-ours!
What?

37
00:01:27.387 --> 00:01:28.923
Let! Me! In!

38
00:01:28.957 --> 00:01:29.991
[ Electricity crackles ]
Owww!

39
00:01:30.024 --> 00:01:30.992
Unh!

40
00:01:31.025 --> 00:01:34.461
M-o-o-o-ort-y-y-y-y!

41
00:01:34.494 --> 00:01:37.331
I mean. Rick. I don't really
know what I can do here.

42
00:01:37.364 --> 00:01:40.034
Y-you don't give a shit
about grandpa. huh?

43
00:01:40.068 --> 00:01:41.301
Is -- Is that it. Morty?
Y-you want me dead?

44
00:01:41.335 --> 00:01:42.737
[ Sighs ]
Rick...

45
00:01:42.770 --> 00:01:45.573
Y-you won't inherit
anything from me. Morty.

46
00:01:45.607 --> 00:01:47.875
Evil boy. Wicked boy.
[ Cellphone ringing ]

47
00:01:47.909 --> 00:01:49.276
Okay.
You know what?

48
00:01:49.309 --> 00:01:51.846
Hello? R-Rick S--
Rick Sanchez phone.

49
00:01:51.879 --> 00:01:53.480
How'd -- How you
get this number?

50
00:01:54.015 --> 00:01:55.415
Reese!
Reese?

51
00:01:55.449 --> 00:01:57.417
Uh. y-you're in town?
Of course we can.

52
00:01:57.451 --> 00:02:00.187
Of course I'm drunk.
L-let's. uh. see you soon!

53
00:02:00.220 --> 00:02:02.389
Guess who that was!
It was Reese.

54
00:02:02.422 --> 00:02:04.092
Y-you said --
You said it out loud!

55
00:02:04.124 --> 00:02:06.027
Fucking Reese. Morty!

56
00:02:06.060 --> 00:02:08.261
Mnhmnh.
who needs passwords. huh?

57
00:02:08.295 --> 00:02:11.331
W-we need our minds
off of this <i>shit.</i> Morty.

58
00:02:11.365 --> 00:02:13.433
We gotta hang out
with our pal Reese!

59
00:02:13.467 --> 00:02:16.070
Rick. you just yelled at me.
and I don't even care.

60
00:02:16.104 --> 00:02:17.639
I like Reese that much.

61
00:02:17.672 --> 00:02:19.674
[burps] That's 'cause
he's the fuckin' best!

62
00:02:19.707 --> 00:02:21.075
You got that right.

63
00:02:21.109 --> 00:02:22.744
[ Downbeat rock music plays ]

64
00:02:22.777 --> 00:02:24.211
♪♪

65
00:02:24.244 --> 00:02:27.548
Reese! Reese! Reese!
Reese! Reese! Reese!

66
00:02:27.582 --> 00:02:37.558
♪♪

67
00:02:37.592 --> 00:02:47.568
♪♪

68
00:02:47.602 --> 00:02:55.242
♪♪

69
00:02:55.275 --> 00:02:56.911
[ Electricity crackles ]

70
00:03:02.249 --> 00:03:03.885
I love these trips. Reese.

71
00:03:03.918 --> 00:03:05.153
H-hell. yeah!

72
00:03:05.185 --> 00:03:06.888
Fly-fishing. babay!

73
00:03:06.921 --> 00:03:07.889
[ Reel whirs ]

74
00:03:07.922 --> 00:03:08.923
[ Snap! ]

75
00:03:08.956 --> 00:03:10.457
Aww!
W-was that my fault?

76
00:03:10.490 --> 00:03:11.959
D-did I
fuck that up?

77
00:03:11.993 --> 00:03:14.162
M-dawg.
if they never got away.

78
00:03:14.194 --> 00:03:15.897
what'd be the point
of catching 'em?

79
00:03:15.930 --> 00:03:19.266
Man. that's some great --
great fly-fishing wisdom. Reese.

80
00:03:19.299 --> 00:03:20.668
Really calming.

81
00:03:20.702 --> 00:03:22.269
You gotta wade
with the current. dude.

82
00:03:22.302 --> 00:03:23.738
You're the best.
[ Reel whirs ]

83
00:03:23.771 --> 00:03:25.506
Awww. geez!

84
00:03:25.540 --> 00:03:26.507
Hey. M-Morty.

85
00:03:26.541 --> 00:03:28.375
Morty. Morty.
Morty. Morty!

86
00:03:28.408 --> 00:03:29.577
Oh! Oh. God!
Rick!

87
00:03:29.610 --> 00:03:31.879
[ Chuckles ]
Get outta here!

88
00:03:31.913 --> 00:03:33.748
[ Laughing ]

89
00:03:33.781 --> 00:03:35.315
[ Insects chirping ]

90
00:03:35.348 --> 00:03:37.484
I <i>know</i> I packed
the special marshmallows.

91
00:03:37.518 --> 00:03:39.587
One job.
I opened the cabinet.

92
00:03:39.620 --> 00:03:41.455
I looked at them.
I <i>know</i> I looked at them!

93
00:03:41.488 --> 00:03:43.024
One job!

94
00:03:43.057 --> 00:03:44.458
You forgot them
on the last Reese trip.

95
00:03:44.491 --> 00:03:46.460
Seems like a bad thing
to trust me with. then.

96
00:03:46.493 --> 00:03:48.596
You gotta be more patient
with Morty. Rick.

97
00:03:48.629 --> 00:03:50.464
Not everyone
can be a genius.

98
00:03:50.497 --> 00:03:54.468
It's what you do with
what you got that counts.

99
00:03:54.502 --> 00:03:56.671
Sorry. Morty.
I could take it easier on you.

100
00:03:56.704 --> 00:03:59.372
I'm. uh -- I'm still wired
from catching all those fish.

101
00:03:59.406 --> 00:04:03.177
Ha ha! Well. you'd find a way
to get high on anything.

102
00:04:03.211 --> 00:04:04.746
Ain't that the truth?

103
00:04:04.779 --> 00:04:06.581
[ All laughing ]

104
00:04:06.614 --> 00:04:07.648
Rick: True.

105
00:04:07.682 --> 00:04:09.550
You know. Rick.
you two may fight.

106
00:04:09.584 --> 00:04:12.153
but you're the real deal.

107
00:04:12.186 --> 00:04:14.354
[ Watch dings ]
Heh. Thanks. Reese.

108
00:04:14.387 --> 00:04:15.523
[ Cellphone vibrates ]

109
00:04:15.556 --> 00:04:17.959
Ah. man.
I hate to do this. guys.

110
00:04:17.992 --> 00:04:20.393
but I got some work stuff
I still need to hit.

111
00:04:20.427 --> 00:04:21.763
Might have to call it.

112
00:04:21.796 --> 00:04:23.631
[burps] Sounds good to me.
I'm beat.

113
00:04:23.664 --> 00:04:25.800
What? The --
The trip just started.

114
00:04:25.833 --> 00:04:28.836
Sorry. champ. but the river's
not going anywhere.

115
00:04:28.870 --> 00:04:32.006
Shake a leg. Morty.
Some of us got
responsibilities.

116
00:04:33.406 --> 00:04:35.408
[ Bottles clattering ]

117
00:04:35.442 --> 00:04:37.310
You could always just
move to Earth. Reese.

118
00:04:37.344 --> 00:04:38.746
Rick's a god.

119
00:04:38.780 --> 00:04:40.347
He could. like.
grow your job out of slime.

120
00:04:40.380 --> 00:04:42.250
He could grow your
whole company out of slime.

121
00:04:42.282 --> 00:04:44.085
It's a great idea. Morty.

122
00:04:44.118 --> 00:04:45.820
I'll pitch it to my boss.

123
00:04:45.853 --> 00:04:47.755
Bye. Reese.

124
00:04:47.789 --> 00:04:50.758
Remember. wade with
the current. pal.

125
00:04:50.792 --> 00:04:53.293
[ Machinery whirring ]
Theft detected.

126
00:04:55.563 --> 00:04:57.965
Um. did -- did --
did you just...

127
00:04:59.399 --> 00:05:01.068
Threat nullified.

128
00:05:01.102 --> 00:05:03.403
Shit.
Jesus fucking Christ!

129
00:05:03.436 --> 00:05:05.606
Okay. so. Morty.
I know your instinct will be

130
00:05:05.640 --> 00:05:07.275
to make a big deal
about this.

131
00:05:07.307 --> 00:05:09.043
You'll be all.
"Betrayal! Betrayal!"

132
00:05:09.076 --> 00:05:10.778
We've known him
for years!

133
00:05:10.812 --> 00:05:14.414
S-so Reese takes us camping
whenever you get locked out?!

134
00:05:14.447 --> 00:05:17.251
Oh. my God.
Am I your fucking password?

135
00:05:17.285 --> 00:05:19.220
Ugh. It's more complex
than that.

136
00:05:19.253 --> 00:05:20.755
But yes.

137
00:05:20.788 --> 00:05:22.590
Our relationship is
unique in the multiverse.

138
00:05:22.623 --> 00:05:24.158
Th-there.
Jerk off to it.

139
00:05:24.192 --> 00:05:25.726
It's what
you <i>always</i> wanted.

140
00:05:25.760 --> 00:05:27.327
We're unique.
and I depend on you.

141
00:05:27.360 --> 00:05:28.461
Unh!
Whoa!

142
00:05:28.495 --> 00:05:30.298
And you needed to gaslight me

143
00:05:30.330 --> 00:05:32.499
with a cool fake friend
to verify that?!

144
00:05:32.533 --> 00:05:34.001
Morty. how can you
be mad at this?

145
00:05:34.035 --> 00:05:36.737
I created an awesome guy
we had a great time with.

146
00:05:36.771 --> 00:05:38.639
I'm more sad about this
than you. Morty.

147
00:05:38.673 --> 00:05:40.508
I liked Reese.
Reese was cool.

148
00:05:40.541 --> 00:05:43.343
Now I gotta build
a new fuckin' Reese thing!

149
00:05:43.376 --> 00:05:44.444
[ Grunting ]

150
00:05:44.477 --> 00:05:46.614
Unh! Hunh!
Uhh! Unh!

151
00:05:46.647 --> 00:05:47.648
Unh!

152
00:05:47.682 --> 00:05:48.448
Aah!

153
00:05:48.481 --> 00:05:52.019
[ Muffled screaming ]

154
00:05:52.053 --> 00:05:55.156
[ Muffled screaming continues ]

155
00:05:55.189 --> 00:05:57.024
Mm. Mm.

156
00:05:57.058 --> 00:06:00.828
Mm. Mm. Mm. Mm.

157
00:06:00.862 --> 00:06:02.096
[ Gulping loudly ]

158
00:06:03.598 --> 00:06:05.398
Ahh. Oh.

159
00:06:05.432 --> 00:06:07.702
[ Gulping continues ]

160
00:06:12.106 --> 00:06:14.876
Ahh.
[ Sighs ]

161
00:06:14.909 --> 00:06:19.446
What?
It's just. how is there
that much liquid in there?

162
00:06:19.479 --> 00:06:22.183
Oh. Uh. this one is. uh --
it's a -- it's a portal thing.

163
00:06:22.216 --> 00:06:24.952
Th-there's a big silo full
of vodka on this one planet.

164
00:06:24.986 --> 00:06:27.655
These. uh. little hog-men
keep it full for me.

165
00:06:27.688 --> 00:06:30.925
Okay.
I'm gonna go
[burps] empty it.

166
00:06:34.061 --> 00:06:35.462
Ugh!

167
00:06:37.899 --> 00:06:39.166
Rick?

168
00:06:39.200 --> 00:06:41.202
That was fucked up. Rick.

169
00:06:41.235 --> 00:06:42.603
But I can handle fucked up.

170
00:06:42.637 --> 00:06:44.972
A-a-and now
that I know what Reese is.

171
00:06:45.006 --> 00:06:48.042
w-we can. we can hang out
with him all the time. right?

172
00:06:48.075 --> 00:06:49.911
Uh...
Morty wha-whaa?

173
00:06:49.944 --> 00:06:52.213
What the hell
are you doing to him?

174
00:06:52.246 --> 00:06:57.718
Oh. I got. I gotta transfer over
some stuff-uh before disposal.

175
00:06:57.752 --> 00:06:58.920
"Disposal"?!

176
00:06:58.953 --> 00:07:01.454
Reese is a liability. Morty.
[ Device beeps ]

177
00:07:01.488 --> 00:07:02.990
He's like a credit card.

178
00:07:03.024 --> 00:07:04.825
If he's not in use.
he-e's gotta be shredded.

179
00:07:04.859 --> 00:07:06.127
Chin up. Morty.

180
00:07:06.160 --> 00:07:09.263
It's my bad for going all
Iron Giant in front of ya.

181
00:07:09.297 --> 00:07:10.497
I don't want
you to die.

182
00:07:10.531 --> 00:07:12.733
Hey. hey. hey.
I'm not dying...

183
00:07:12.767 --> 00:07:14.467
'cause I was never
really living.

184
00:07:14.502 --> 00:07:16.604
[ Slurring ] He's got all
my passwords. Morty.

185
00:07:16.637 --> 00:07:19.840
You can't just -- he's not
a guy. he's -- he's a wallet.

186
00:07:19.874 --> 00:07:20.908
Nice wallet.

187
00:07:20.942 --> 00:07:22.510
Aah! Morty!

188
00:07:22.543 --> 00:07:24.378
[ Errors dinging ]

189
00:07:24.412 --> 00:07:26.247
<i>Lockdown initiated.</i>

190
00:07:26.280 --> 00:07:27.447
[ Machinery whirring ]

191
00:07:27.480 --> 00:07:28.950
Morty. nooo!

192
00:07:30.084 --> 00:07:32.019
Aah! Ooh! Ohh!

193
00:07:32.053 --> 00:07:33.486
[ Groans ]

194
00:07:33.521 --> 00:07:35.990
[ Pounding on hatch ]

195
00:07:36.023 --> 00:07:37.425
[ Honking. horn blares ]

196
00:07:37.457 --> 00:07:39.727
[ Meow! Bonk! ]
[ Man yodeling ]

197
00:07:39.760 --> 00:07:41.494
[ Intercom static ]
Reese is my <i>friend!</i>

198
00:07:41.529 --> 00:07:42.997
Rick:
<i>He's not</i> alive. <i>Morty!</i>

199
00:07:43.030 --> 00:07:45.666
He's-- he's a program
that unlocks my computer

200
00:07:45.700 --> 00:07:47.268
and dispenses clichés!

201
00:07:47.301 --> 00:07:49.236
<i>You better open</i>
<i>that hatch. Morty!</i>

202
00:07:53.207 --> 00:07:54.608
[ Switch clicks ]

203
00:07:54.642 --> 00:07:57.078
Reese?
Ar-are you okay?

204
00:07:57.111 --> 00:07:58.212
Whoa!

205
00:07:58.245 --> 00:07:59.680
I'm a bit worried.

206
00:07:59.714 --> 00:08:01.749
I mean. what happens
when Rick reels us in?

207
00:08:01.782 --> 00:08:03.451
Guess I can drop
the folksy act.

208
00:08:03.483 --> 00:08:05.786
No. I-I like it.
It's part of the charm.

209
00:08:05.820 --> 00:08:07.521
Well. then where are
we casting off?

210
00:08:07.555 --> 00:08:09.056
There's an old
landline portal down here.

211
00:08:09.090 --> 00:08:10.691
Level 17.

212
00:08:10.725 --> 00:08:12.059
W-we'll figure it out
from there.

213
00:08:12.093 --> 00:08:13.728
Aye-aye. Captain!

214
00:08:14.295 --> 00:08:16.263
Maybe a lighter touch.

215
00:08:18.032 --> 00:08:19.734
[ Device powering up ]

216
00:08:20.935 --> 00:08:21.969
Aah!

217
00:08:25.272 --> 00:08:27.341
Neighbor: Ohh!!
The TV froze!

218
00:08:27.375 --> 00:08:28.876
Now what do I think?!

219
00:08:33.114 --> 00:08:35.016
[ Line ringing ]

220
00:08:35.049 --> 00:08:36.884
Huge Clouds Metallurgy.

221
00:08:36.917 --> 00:08:39.153
Rick: <i>You guys</i>
<i>helped me build a lock.</i>

222
00:08:39.186 --> 00:08:40.821
That's right. we did.

223
00:08:40.855 --> 00:08:42.289
Rick: <i>I locked it</i>
<i>with the keys inside.</i>

224
00:08:42.323 --> 00:08:44.558
That is gonna take
some metallurgy.

225
00:08:44.592 --> 00:08:46.994
You said it. How soon can
your technician get here?

226
00:08:47.028 --> 00:08:49.930
<i>Hmm. We need</i>
<i>remote system access.</i>

227
00:08:49.964 --> 00:08:51.732
Can do. One sec.

228
00:08:51.766 --> 00:08:53.234
Hey. Jerry. call for you.

229
00:08:53.267 --> 00:08:57.338
Yello--
ooughughuhglugughh!

230
00:08:57.371 --> 00:08:58.873
Ho-ho-hoo-hoo!

231
00:08:58.906 --> 00:09:00.708
Yeah. yeah. you're
a bipedal simian now.

232
00:09:00.741 --> 00:09:04.211
in a gravity of 9.8 MPS.
Don't. don't get any ideas.

233
00:09:04.245 --> 00:09:06.714
So much m-a-a-a-ass.

234
00:09:08.582 --> 00:09:11.952
Sorry. sorry.
You said the lock was...?

235
00:09:14.755 --> 00:09:16.057
This is interesting.

236
00:09:16.090 --> 00:09:18.626
We don't sell this model
double-bonded.

237
00:09:18.659 --> 00:09:21.028
I know.
Did that a-ma-self.

238
00:09:21.062 --> 00:09:22.096
[ Whistles ]

239
00:09:22.129 --> 00:09:24.665
This is qu-a-a-ality work.

240
00:09:24.698 --> 00:09:25.900
Oh. thanks.
Heh.

241
00:09:25.933 --> 00:09:28.836
Of course.
it does void the warranty.

242
00:09:28.869 --> 00:09:32.339
What?
I'll need access
to this whole thing.

243
00:09:32.373 --> 00:09:34.275
Might have to
dig it all out.

244
00:09:34.308 --> 00:09:37.578
Is there a place where I could
get tools and things?

245
00:09:37.611 --> 00:09:39.447
For this?
A hardware store?

246
00:09:39.480 --> 00:09:41.582
Yes...
And you're
not just stalling

247
00:09:41.615 --> 00:09:43.250
'cause you wanna
take this new body out

248
00:09:43.284 --> 00:09:44.919
for a sensory
flight of fancy?

249
00:09:44.952 --> 00:09:46.821
Noooo...

250
00:09:47.721 --> 00:09:50.291
Remember.
whole subbasement!

251
00:09:50.324 --> 00:09:52.359
Dug out!
Whoo-hoo-hoo!

252
00:09:53.661 --> 00:09:55.629
Should be
a straight shot to 17.

253
00:09:55.663 --> 00:09:57.098
Just have to...

254
00:09:57.131 --> 00:09:59.066
c-cut. cut through
the prison level...

255
00:09:59.100 --> 00:10:01.469
[ Ominous music plays ]

256
00:10:01.503 --> 00:10:03.838
Hey. those weapons
you used earlier to. uh.

257
00:10:03.871 --> 00:10:05.606
kill that raccoon --
Destroy the intruder.

258
00:10:05.639 --> 00:10:07.408
Destroy the intruder!
That's better.

259
00:10:07.441 --> 00:10:09.578
Uh. can you use those...
whenever?

260
00:10:09.610 --> 00:10:10.945
Not really.

261
00:10:10.978 --> 00:10:12.313
I mean. just on things
that threaten you.

262
00:10:12.346 --> 00:10:13.848
the house. or Rick.

263
00:10:13.881 --> 00:10:18.119
So you can destroy things
that are hurting me.

264
00:10:19.487 --> 00:10:20.522
Yes.

265
00:10:20.555 --> 00:10:22.756
Aw. geez.

266
00:10:22.790 --> 00:10:24.258
[ Inhales deeply ]

267
00:10:24.291 --> 00:10:26.627
Unh! Unh!
Unh! Unh!

268
00:10:26.660 --> 00:10:27.895
[ Whirring ]

269
00:10:29.330 --> 00:10:31.699
Threat nullified.

270
00:10:31.732 --> 00:10:33.568
[ Groans ]
Here we go.

271
00:10:33.602 --> 00:10:36.070
There should be no shortage
of threats in here.

272
00:10:37.572 --> 00:10:39.473
Thank fucking God.

273
00:10:39.508 --> 00:10:40.908
That was gonna suck.

274
00:10:40.941 --> 00:10:43.210
Aw. I was fixing
to have me a hootenanny

275
00:10:43.244 --> 00:10:44.245
like you wouldn't believe.

276
00:10:44.278 --> 00:10:45.746
Revenge!!
Aah!

277
00:10:48.649 --> 00:10:50.585
He grabbed your leg
and screamed "revenge."

278
00:10:50.619 --> 00:10:52.319
No. no.
a-all that buildup.

279
00:10:52.353 --> 00:10:54.855
I'm glad
<i>something</i> happened.

280
00:10:54.889 --> 00:10:57.992
Morty I -- I don't actually know
what "hootenanny" means.

281
00:10:58.025 --> 00:11:00.127
It's okay.
We're almost there.

282
00:11:00.161 --> 00:11:01.295
[ Drill whirring ]

283
00:11:03.632 --> 00:11:04.732
Where the fuck
is that guy?

284
00:11:04.765 --> 00:11:06.300
Beth: D-a-a-ad?

285
00:11:06.333 --> 00:11:08.637
Where's Jerry?!

286
00:11:08.669 --> 00:11:11.205
Rick: That's exactly
what I'm wondering!

287
00:11:12.206 --> 00:11:13.575
[ Cellphone vibrating ]

288
00:11:13.608 --> 00:11:16.511
[ Humming ]
Hello?

289
00:11:16.545 --> 00:11:18.712
That doesn't sound
like a hardware store.

290
00:11:18.746 --> 00:11:20.748
Uh. it is!

291
00:11:20.781 --> 00:11:22.750
[ Giggles ]

292
00:11:22.783 --> 00:11:25.186
[ Laughing ]

293
00:11:25.219 --> 00:11:27.154
[ Giggling ]

294
00:11:27.188 --> 00:11:28.455
You let anyone do that?

295
00:11:28.489 --> 00:11:30.291
He gave us
all the money he had.

296
00:11:31.593 --> 00:11:34.195
[ Banging ]
Morty: Hunh! Hunh! Hunh!

297
00:11:35.462 --> 00:11:37.298
Threat nullified.

298
00:11:37.331 --> 00:11:38.667
Hey. how 's your head?

299
00:11:38.699 --> 00:11:41.001
M-my vision's gettin'
pretty cloudy.

300
00:11:41.035 --> 00:11:45.039
B-but even I can see. heh.
y-you're almost free. Reese!

301
00:11:45.072 --> 00:11:46.675
[ Door creaks ]

302
00:11:46.707 --> 00:11:48.876
Yes! We're getting you
out of here!

303
00:11:51.513 --> 00:11:52.880
[ Engine starts ]

304
00:11:52.913 --> 00:11:56.217
[ Portal device whirring.
modem buzzing ]

305
00:11:56.250 --> 00:11:57.686
[ Ding! ]

306
00:11:57.718 --> 00:11:59.820
Ohh. that looks nice.

307
00:11:59.853 --> 00:12:02.189
Good.
Then that's your new home.

308
00:12:02.223 --> 00:12:04.358
[ Portal hums ]

309
00:12:06.794 --> 00:12:08.530
Wow.
Huh.

310
00:12:08.563 --> 00:12:11.131
Expected a different
kind of catfish.

311
00:12:11.165 --> 00:12:12.466
Uh. 'scuse me.

312
00:12:12.499 --> 00:12:14.268
Is there still forest
around here?

313
00:12:14.301 --> 00:12:15.670
Whassat?
Oh. no.

314
00:12:15.704 --> 00:12:18.372
Not since the God
in the White Coat.

315
00:12:18.405 --> 00:12:21.643
He gave our world the gift
of metal and computer science.

316
00:12:21.676 --> 00:12:24.679
In return.
we run his holy silo.

317
00:12:24.713 --> 00:12:26.747
The younger hogs
resent our duty.

318
00:12:26.780 --> 00:12:29.183
Can't say I blame 'em.
If wages keep stagnatin'.

319
00:12:29.216 --> 00:12:31.085
maybe I'll do something worse!
Ha ha!

320
00:12:31.118 --> 00:12:34.054
Oh. wow. Yeah.
that-th-that guy's my grandpa.

321
00:12:34.088 --> 00:12:36.725
Th-this is Reese.
He. uh. he works for him. too.

322
00:12:36.757 --> 00:12:38.025
The password man.

323
00:12:38.058 --> 00:12:39.827
Oh. I may be
putting down roots here.

324
00:12:39.860 --> 00:12:41.829
Please do!
Now. if y'all excuse me.

325
00:12:41.862 --> 00:12:45.065
I'm needed at a high-tech
potato distillery.

326
00:12:45.099 --> 00:12:47.268
Well.
w-w-we did it. Reese.

327
00:12:47.301 --> 00:12:49.203
It's the first day
of the rest of your life.

328
00:12:49.236 --> 00:12:51.805
Before today. I was
a two-factor authenticator

329
00:12:51.839 --> 00:12:53.508
with a vague
Southern affect.

330
00:12:53.541 --> 00:12:55.876
Now I can be
whatever I want.

331
00:12:55.909 --> 00:12:59.079
Thank you. Morty.
Uh. y-y-you're welcome.
Reese.

332
00:12:59.113 --> 00:13:02.049
Wade with the current.
I'll probably
do somethin' else.

333
00:13:02.082 --> 00:13:04.785
Fishing's b-o-o-o-o-ring!

334
00:13:04.818 --> 00:13:06.588
[ Footsteps approaching ]

335
00:13:06.621 --> 00:13:08.088
Busy store.

336
00:13:08.122 --> 00:13:11.292
Plus. I had to run
with these <i>weird</i> legs.

337
00:13:13.628 --> 00:13:17.831
[ Humming. thunder crashes ]

338
00:13:20.267 --> 00:13:22.236
There we go.

339
00:13:22.269 --> 00:13:25.172
Bro. you made me dig
out the whole thing.

340
00:13:25.774 --> 00:13:27.509
Oh! Hey. hey. Rick.

341
00:13:27.542 --> 00:13:30.210
God damn it. Morty!
We just cracked the lock!

342
00:13:30.244 --> 00:13:31.879
Now I have to pay
this guy his full rate!

343
00:13:31.912 --> 00:13:34.516
I am <i>very</i> expensive.

344
00:13:34.549 --> 00:13:36.785
Where's Reese?
Safe from you!

345
00:13:36.817 --> 00:13:38.485
I took him through
the landline portal

346
00:13:38.520 --> 00:13:41.322
and set him up with a new life
with his new hog friends.

347
00:13:41.355 --> 00:13:42.323
Oh. no.

348
00:13:42.356 --> 00:13:46.427
[ Machinery whirring ]

349
00:13:46.460 --> 00:13:50.197
<i>Rick Sanchez. we have</i>
<i>taken possession of</i>
<i>your password man.</i>

350
00:13:50.230 --> 00:13:52.366
<i>Long live</i>
<i>the Hog Resistance!</i>

351
00:13:52.399 --> 00:13:53.901
Morty. you dumb idiot.

352
00:13:53.934 --> 00:13:56.270
you think those vodka hogs
wouldn't fuck me over?

353
00:13:56.303 --> 00:13:58.673
Th-the good-natured
rustic thing is just an act!

354
00:13:58.707 --> 00:14:04.244
Their whole planet
runs on my tech. Morty!

355
00:14:04.278 --> 00:14:05.547
Whoaaaa!

356
00:14:05.580 --> 00:14:07.848
Wooooh!
Ooohahh! Ohh!

357
00:14:07.881 --> 00:14:09.216
I'm gonna fuckin' barf!

358
00:14:12.554 --> 00:14:16.223
<i>Rick Sanchez. you will</i>
<i>no longer subjugate</i>
<i>our homeworld!</i>

359
00:14:16.256 --> 00:14:17.424
<i>Fuck you!</i>

360
00:14:17.458 --> 00:14:19.661
-Go make my vodka!
<i>-No!</i>

361
00:14:19.694 --> 00:14:21.796
<i>We just got access</i>
<i>to your desktop...</i>

362
00:14:21.830 --> 00:14:24.398
<i>Deh? Ooh. are these</i>
<i>circles fucking?</i>

363
00:14:24.431 --> 00:14:25.767
They're making love!

364
00:14:25.800 --> 00:14:27.602
IT guy. rip that computer out!

365
00:14:29.269 --> 00:14:31.004
[ Gunfire ]

366
00:14:33.207 --> 00:14:35.242
[ Screaming in the distance ]
Are Summer and Mom home?

367
00:14:35.275 --> 00:14:37.378
F-u-u-u-u-uck!

368
00:14:39.581 --> 00:14:41.081
Morty. grab on!

369
00:14:42.684 --> 00:14:45.052
-Wh-o-o-o-oa!
-Aaaah!

370
00:14:46.755 --> 00:14:48.656
[ Both grunting ]

371
00:14:50.157 --> 00:14:51.191
Aah!

372
00:14:52.326 --> 00:14:54.094
Why is the
furniture attacking us?

373
00:14:54.128 --> 00:14:55.797
Rick's been hacked!

374
00:14:55.830 --> 00:14:57.565
Because Morty assumed
that hogs in overalls

375
00:14:57.599 --> 00:14:59.266
couldn't also be hackers!

376
00:14:59.299 --> 00:15:00.334
Aah!

377
00:15:04.773 --> 00:15:06.808
Um. Dad. you're losing
a lot of blood.

378
00:15:06.841 --> 00:15:09.577
It's okay!
I can make more!

379
00:15:09.611 --> 00:15:10.812
Badass.

380
00:15:10.845 --> 00:15:13.914
♪♪

381
00:15:13.947 --> 00:15:16.150
Stop replacing my stuff
with robots!

382
00:15:16.183 --> 00:15:17.719
You never noticed
the difference!

383
00:15:17.752 --> 00:15:20.020
<i>Rick lies to everyone!</i>

384
00:15:20.053 --> 00:15:22.389
<i>Doesn't that make</i>
<i>you wanna join the resistance?</i>

385
00:15:27.094 --> 00:15:28.929
Shit!
The floor is lava!

386
00:15:28.962 --> 00:15:30.732
Did you put that in
for defense or for fun?

387
00:15:30.765 --> 00:15:32.132
I don't remember!

388
00:15:32.166 --> 00:15:34.134
Ooh-hoo-ho-hoo!
Ho-ho-ho!

389
00:15:34.168 --> 00:15:35.737
You ever think about how
instead of wrapping yourself

390
00:15:35.770 --> 00:15:37.572
in infinite
layers of defense

391
00:15:37.605 --> 00:15:38.873
you could just
be nicer to people?
[ Cellphone ringing ]

392
00:15:38.907 --> 00:15:40.340
Never once. Morty!

393
00:15:41.743 --> 00:15:45.112
Hog Hacker: <i>Rick Sanchez.</i>
<i>is your refrigerator running?</i>

394
00:15:45.145 --> 00:15:46.915
<i>Because you better</i>
<i>go and catch it!</i>

395
00:15:46.947 --> 00:15:48.716
You owe me.

396
00:15:48.750 --> 00:15:50.484
Wh-o-o-oa!

397
00:15:50.518 --> 00:15:51.985
[ Laughing ]

398
00:15:52.019 --> 00:15:53.755
Ooh-ugh-ah!

399
00:15:53.788 --> 00:15:54.889
Whoa-ho-ho-ho!

400
00:15:54.923 --> 00:15:56.691
Everyone. kill yourselves!

401
00:15:56.724 --> 00:15:58.726
I'll help!
Huh?

402
00:15:58.760 --> 00:16:01.328
<i>[ Screaming. squelching ]</i>

403
00:16:01.361 --> 00:16:03.030
[ Jerry crying ]

404
00:16:03.063 --> 00:16:05.365
Listen to this.
It's the ocean or something.

405
00:16:05.399 --> 00:16:06.500
[ Whimpering ]

406
00:16:06.534 --> 00:16:09.036
Ohh-ugh. uhh!

407
00:16:10.370 --> 00:16:11.806
Thanks for
turning off the lava.

408
00:16:11.840 --> 00:16:13.240
[ All grunting ]

409
00:16:13.273 --> 00:16:14.676
You couldn't have
turned off everything?

410
00:16:14.709 --> 00:16:15.743
Ohh!

411
00:16:22.817 --> 00:16:23.918
[ Roars ]

412
00:16:23.952 --> 00:16:26.053
Emergency shutoff in my room.

413
00:16:26.654 --> 00:16:27.689
Run!

414
00:16:28.957 --> 00:16:30.457
Oh-ho-ho!
Ooh!

415
00:16:33.460 --> 00:16:34.796
Aaaah! Aaaaah! Unf!

416
00:16:34.829 --> 00:16:36.196
I hate living here!

417
00:16:36.230 --> 00:16:37.732
-Aaaaaaaaaah!
-Move!

418
00:16:39.266 --> 00:16:41.335
Hit that shut-off quick.
It stinks in here.

419
00:16:41.368 --> 00:16:42.937
Punching down.

420
00:16:42.971 --> 00:16:44.204
[ Zap! ]

421
00:16:44.238 --> 00:16:46.173
[ Electricity crackles ]

422
00:16:51.011 --> 00:16:53.548
-See? All fixed.
-Awesome.

423
00:16:54.782 --> 00:16:57.184
Th-thank goodness
you knocked out all that stuff.

424
00:16:57.217 --> 00:16:58.553
Yep.
Nothing electronic left

425
00:16:58.586 --> 00:17:00.622
that can be hacked
or turned against us.

426
00:17:00.655 --> 00:17:01.723
Salud!

427
00:17:01.756 --> 00:17:03.490
Ohh!
Aah!

428
00:17:08.262 --> 00:17:10.865
The Liberation of Hog Planet
is at hand.

429
00:17:10.899 --> 00:17:13.601
Prepare for your death.
Oppressor Sanchez.

430
00:17:13.635 --> 00:17:14.769
Reese. no!

431
00:17:16.236 --> 00:17:17.404
Run!

432
00:17:18.105 --> 00:17:19.541
Whoa.
New look for Reese.

433
00:17:19.574 --> 00:17:22.242
I don't like how many
adult friends Morty has.

434
00:17:25.513 --> 00:17:26.648
Gyaah!

435
00:17:26.681 --> 00:17:28.148
Rick.
use your implants!

436
00:17:28.181 --> 00:17:29.851
What part of
"nothing electronic"

437
00:17:29.884 --> 00:17:31.151
went over your head.
Morty?

438
00:17:31.184 --> 00:17:32.654
Hit him with pipes!

439
00:17:32.687 --> 00:17:35.255
[ Both grunting ]

440
00:17:35.289 --> 00:17:37.257
It's not doing anything!

441
00:17:37.291 --> 00:17:38.325
Whoa!

442
00:17:38.993 --> 00:17:40.394
-Aah!
-Aah!

443
00:17:42.730 --> 00:17:44.064
Oh!

444
00:17:44.097 --> 00:17:46.433
Sorry I'm d-doing this.
R-Rick.

445
00:17:46.466 --> 00:17:49.202
I think someone messed
with my h-h-head.

446
00:17:49.236 --> 00:17:50.838
Reese. it's me!
Remember?

447
00:17:50.872 --> 00:17:52.205
You told me it was normal

448
00:17:52.239 --> 00:17:53.875
to have one pube longer
than the others?

449
00:17:53.908 --> 00:17:56.109
Stop trying to override his
programming with love. Morty!

450
00:17:56.143 --> 00:17:57.879
Well. hitting him with pipes
isn't working!

451
00:17:57.912 --> 00:17:59.179
Ow!

452
00:18:00.147 --> 00:18:02.482
You can't love something
out of hurting you!

453
00:18:02.517 --> 00:18:03.885
Oh. you'd sure love
that to be true!

454
00:18:03.918 --> 00:18:05.053
Fuck you. Morty!

455
00:18:05.085 --> 00:18:06.521
-I hate you!
-I hate you!

456
00:18:06.554 --> 00:18:08.690
-I hate you! I hate you!
-I hate you! I hate you!

457
00:18:08.723 --> 00:18:10.825
I hate you! I hate you!
I hate you!
I hate you! I hate you!

458
00:18:10.858 --> 00:18:13.728
I hate you!
I hate you! I hate you!
I hate you!

459
00:18:13.761 --> 00:18:15.262
[ Electricity crackles ]
Unh!

460
00:18:15.295 --> 00:18:16.631
Ahh.

461
00:18:16.664 --> 00:18:19.466
Y-y-you know what. Rick?
You two may f-f-fight.

462
00:18:19.499 --> 00:18:23.037
but you're the real d-d-deal.

463
00:18:23.071 --> 00:18:24.304
[ Machinery whirring down ]

464
00:18:26.874 --> 00:18:29.176
[ Armor clanking ]

465
00:18:30.678 --> 00:18:31.913
Huh.

466
00:18:31.946 --> 00:18:33.848
Probably
doesn't mean anything.

467
00:18:34.949 --> 00:18:36.216
Yep.

468
00:18:40.655 --> 00:18:43.357
[ Rumbling ]

469
00:18:43.390 --> 00:18:46.126
Hey. Grandpa. did you turn
the yard into a giant sinkhole

470
00:18:46.159 --> 00:18:47.394
when you dug out
the subbasement?

471
00:18:47.427 --> 00:18:48.997
It's fine.
It's just some tunnels.

472
00:18:49.030 --> 00:18:50.765
Are the tunnels
reinforced?

473
00:18:50.798 --> 00:18:53.166
Don't overthink the tunnels.
I have a handle on the tunnels.

474
00:18:53.200 --> 00:18:55.703
[ Vehicle beeping ]

475
00:18:59.641 --> 00:19:02.275
How much longer
is he gonna be Dad for?

476
00:19:02.309 --> 00:19:03.745
I like him.
Me too.

477
00:19:03.778 --> 00:19:05.813
Summer just taught me
what "push-ups" are.

478
00:19:05.847 --> 00:19:08.181
I did.
He's fuckin' nailing them.

479
00:19:08.215 --> 00:19:10.450
-Mom?
-Oh. Uh. one more week?

480
00:19:10.484 --> 00:19:13.387
-What?
-No. no. you're right.

481
00:19:13.420 --> 00:19:16.958
It was good getting to know you.
"The Smiths."

482
00:19:16.991 --> 00:19:19.226
Wait!
Morty. him leaving
was your idea.

483
00:19:19.259 --> 00:19:21.729
Well.
I have another idea.

484
00:19:26.901 --> 00:19:27.869
[ Breathes ]

485
00:19:27.902 --> 00:19:30.638
[ Both scream ]

486
00:19:30.672 --> 00:19:33.273
Ugh!!
Why do I taste rainbow wax?

487
00:19:33.306 --> 00:19:35.442
Why do you know what
that tastes like?

488
00:19:36.443 --> 00:19:37.845
[ Bones crack ]
Oh. Ah!

489
00:19:37.879 --> 00:19:38.946
[ Grunting ]

490
00:19:38.980 --> 00:19:40.480
How 's it feel?

491
00:19:40.515 --> 00:19:43.316
Not as wet as the last guy.
but I'll fix that.

492
00:19:43.350 --> 00:19:47.254
[ Grunting. lips smacking ]

493
00:19:47.287 --> 00:19:49.256
I'm glad you're getting
to live on. Reese.

494
00:19:49.289 --> 00:19:52.126
And getting a pretty sweet rig
out of the deal.

495
00:19:52.160 --> 00:19:54.227
I hope you have
a good life out there.

496
00:19:54.261 --> 00:19:56.164
I...
I love you.

497
00:19:56.196 --> 00:19:59.232
And I love how much matter
you're made of.

498
00:19:59.266 --> 00:20:01.869
I'm leaving now. to do things
that are my business.

499
00:20:01.903 --> 00:20:04.172
There is a place called Skyzone.

500
00:20:04.204 --> 00:20:05.973
Do not visit me there.

501
00:20:07.141 --> 00:20:08.543
[ Sighs ]

502
00:20:08.576 --> 00:20:10.277
What. you gonna keep
sighing until I notice?

503
00:20:10.310 --> 00:20:12.113
I'm just breathing.
He's alive. Morty.

504
00:20:12.146 --> 00:20:13.748
You're welcome.

505
00:20:15.116 --> 00:20:17.151
Gaaaah!
Fuckin' hogs.

506
00:20:17.185 --> 00:20:18.553
Fuckin' Morty.

507
00:20:18.586 --> 00:20:19.554
Cost me a flask.

508
00:20:19.587 --> 00:20:20.722
[ Beep! ]

509
00:20:20.755 --> 00:20:22.422
[ Explosions.
Hog-people screaming ]

510
00:20:22.456 --> 00:20:25.093
[burps] Learned my lesson.
No more portal flasks.

511
00:20:25.126 --> 00:20:26.728
Mmm. mmm!

512
00:20:26.761 --> 00:20:28.963
Ahh.

513
00:20:28.996 --> 00:20:31.933
Mmm. mmm.
Mmm.

514
00:20:31.966 --> 00:20:33.034
Ahh.

515
00:20:33.067 --> 00:20:36.170
Mmm. mmm. mmm.

516
00:20:36.204 --> 00:20:39.207
[burps] Morty. I-I
can tell you're disgusted...

517
00:20:39.239 --> 00:20:40.474
[ Burps ]

518
00:20:40.508 --> 00:20:42.543
...but you're gonna be
just like me!

519
00:20:42.577 --> 00:20:45.412
It's a disease. Morty!
A genetic disease!

520
00:20:45.445 --> 00:20:47.148
It's already in you.
Morty!

521
00:20:47.181 --> 00:20:57.158
♪♪

522
00:20:57.191 --> 00:21:07.168
♪♪

523
00:21:07.201 --> 00:21:17.178
♪♪

524
00:21:17.211 --> 00:21:18.246
[ Groaning ]

525
00:21:18.278 --> 00:21:20.380
H-hey. buddy. y-you good?

526
00:21:20.413 --> 00:21:23.851
F-u-u-uck you. Morty.
you little piece of shit.

527
00:21:23.885 --> 00:21:25.418
You think you're better
than me. Morty?!

528
00:21:25.452 --> 00:21:26.754
I'm gonna --
I'm gonna kill you!

529
00:21:26.788 --> 00:21:28.122
I-I'll kill you!!
[ Knock on door ]

530
00:21:28.156 --> 00:21:29.524
Hey. guys! I'm Rex.

531
00:21:29.557 --> 00:21:31.259
I just moved in next door.

532
00:21:31.291 --> 00:21:33.161
and I love "Minecraft"
and skateboarding!

533
00:21:33.194 --> 00:21:34.294
-Unh!
-Aah!

534
00:21:34.327 --> 00:21:35.863
[ Groaning ]

535
00:21:35.897 --> 00:21:37.464
Aaah! Aah!

536
00:21:37.497 --> 00:21:40.968
Wait- wait. he's- he's not--
[ Cellphone ringing ]

537
00:21:41.002 --> 00:21:42.537
Georgie Boy!

538
00:21:42.570 --> 00:21:45.907
M-Morty. w-would-- would
you believe my unrelated friend.

539
00:21:45.940 --> 00:21:48.209
Georgie Boy.
wants to hang?

540
00:21:48.242 --> 00:21:49.577
Howdy. fellas!

541
00:21:49.610 --> 00:21:51.813
Georgie Boy!
Georgie Boy!
But -- Oh...

542
00:21:51.846 --> 00:21:53.815
Georgie Boy!
Georgie Boy!

543
00:21:55.183 --> 00:21:56.818
Did you get any of that?

